    public interface WritableProperty<V>
extends WritableObservableValue<V>, ReadableProperty<V>, UnmarshallableObject
    A property with write access (e.g. WritableValue.set(Object)). However, it can still be read-only preventing modifications.
    Since:
    1.0.0
